{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 66,
  "title": "第六十六章（江海）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "江海所以能為百浴王者，"
    },
    {
      "text": "以亓善下之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以能為百浴王。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以聖人之："
    },
    {
      "text": "欲上民也，必以亓言下之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "欲先民也，必以亓身後之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "故："
    },
    {
      "text": "居前而民弗害也，"
    },
    {
      "text": "居上而民弗重也。"
    },
    {
      "text": "天下樂推而弗猒也。"
    },
    {
      "text": "非以亓无諍與，"
    },
    {
      "text": "故天下莫能與諍"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 8,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "江海以卑，故眾流歸之，若民歸就王。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 8,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以卑下，故能為百谷王也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 7,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "欲在民之上也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 7,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "法江海處謙虛。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 20,
          "end": 21
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "欲在民之前也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 7,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "先人而後己也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 7,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人在民上為主，不以尊貴虐下，故民戴而不為重。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 7,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人在民前，不以光明蔽後，民親之若父母，無有欲害之心也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 7,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人恩深愛厚，視民如赤子，故天下樂推進以為主，無有厭也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 7,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天下無厭聖人時，是由聖人不與人爭先後也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 7,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言人皆有為，無有與吾爭無為。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
